[metadata]
Name:Forestwalk — Cat Warriors unblockable while opponent has Forest
Goal:Win
Turns:2
Difficulty:Easy
Description:Cat Warriors (2/2 Forestwalk, K:Landwalk:Forest) attacks. The defending player controls a Forest and a Grizzly Bears (2/2). Because the defending player controls a Forest, Cat Warriors has Forestwalk and CANNOT be blocked (CR 702.14a). The 2 damage must hit the player, dropping them from 2 to 0. Before the fix, K:Landwalk:Forest was not correctly applied to the blocking check and the Grizzly Bears would be offered as a legal blocker.

